name: Large DJ Headphones Pendant Necklace
description:
This rockin' three dimensional headphones pendant necklace is highly detailed, attention grabbing and handcrafted for a one of a kind style! Made from polished brass with fully three-dimensional vintage tooling and hung from a vintage gold chain. Chain measures approximately 20" long with a toggle clasp, and can be adjusted by request. Headphones pendant measures about 2" tall and 2.5 wide, and features realistic design and subtle crystal accents. One of my favorite designs I've done yet, this necklace is designed to be worn by both men and women. Rock!

name: Death Metal Twin Guitars Rockstar Necklace
description:
Rock out with this limited edition hardcore electric guitar pendant necklace from Decibel's 2010 Rockstar Collection. Featuring twin metal guitars made from finished steel with engraved flame design. Dark and edgy but with the perfect mix of class and badass. Get ready to fight of droves off screaming fangirls, this necklace is drop dead sexy on both men and women. 

Pendant measures 1.5" long and is suspended from a dark silver chain measuring approximately 20" long with a 4" extender and lobster clasp. Length adjustment of plus or minus a few inches are complimentary, just let me know at checkout. Safe for sensitive skin.

On sale now!

name: Retro Bling Cassette Tape Pendant Necklace
description:
Show of your old school style and pay tribute to retro music with this handcrafted jeweled Cassette Necklace by Decibel. Remember when tapes were all the rage and suddenly opened up the world of music to something that you could record, copy and carry around with you? Relive some of your best nostalgic music times, or pretend you were old enough to remember a world with the iPod with this limited edition necklace.

Featuring a solid and realistic design, this handcrafted pendant is made from polished gold metal and is accented with delicate glass crystals for a subtle bling effect. Measures about 1.5" wide and 1.2" tall and is hung from a gorgeous 16" gold chain with a lobster clasp. Chain length adjustments are complimentary for +/- a few inches, just let me know at checkout. Designed for men or women. Rock!
